13. Re8 {To illustrate, how quickly Black can lose the game. If Black doesn't blunder the idea, the white knight from e3 can proceed to g4, with the typical ideas.} 
14. Nxd5
14. exd5
15. e6
15. Qb6
16. exf7+ {Instead of recapturing the minor piece on d7, White goes for an attack. This trick might work on more than one occasion.} 
16. Kxf7
